{"type": "article", "id": 43929, "title": "给我个“电话亭”，好好工作不是问题｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-09T23:13:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 37711, "name": "Today Is Art Day"}, {"id": 43083, "name": "Killspencer"}, {"id": 43084, "name": "Framery"}, {"id": 43085, "name": "four eight five"}, {"id": 43086, "name": "Giken"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170810071728vTJ5SpbxmhGP03OX.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Utility Belt by Killspencer</h3><p>相信你一定没少见过在腰间别上钥匙圈或是其他小物的行为，它们多少总会让人产生一些违和感。为了让别东西这件事变得更美观，来自洛杉矶的配饰品牌 <a href=\"https://killspencer.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Killspencer</a> 开发了像是特工专用的皮带。这条 Utility Belt 采用了目前正在申请专利的锁扣机制，搭扣固定之后只有往特定的方向拉伸才能解锁，确保放在口袋中的物品不会丢失。这是它的<a href=\"https://killspencer.com/products/utility-belt\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 155 美元起，与绳子配套的卡片夹以及手机套等配件都需要额外购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184117q4WDu5yNnPGcF2Zb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184117kY0PW3oRLjbuiTXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617284\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017080918411835p8jetGMg2TrWv9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184119aHZ1p3JxEtkI8gr9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184117QLetz94mra8id6Sn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623437\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Old Masters action figures by Today Is Art Day</h3><p>还记得头大身小版的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37865.html\">梵高</a>和<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/40785.html\">弗里达</a>玩偶吗？经过两次成功的众筹，来自加拿大的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/todayisartday/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Today Is Art Day</a> 决定继续他们为艺术赋予趣味的目标。在最新的 Old Masters 中，他们一口气将达芬奇、维米尔和伦勃朗这三位著名画家打造成了可爱的玩偶。除了迷你代表作和画框在内的“标配”附件之外，他们也没忘记加入彩蛋：达芬奇的头发和胡子具备了夜光效果、维米尔手握着一对白色珍珠耳环（《戴珍珠耳环的少女》）、伦勃朗则拥有三种根据自画像设计的可替换面部。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/todayisartday/leonardo-da-vinci-vermeer-and-rembrandt-action-fig\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 30 加元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184148xNTMOXV4S7cWvgwZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184148OLAK7ebuwBmZSRhD.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184148NOa826z5xWSjAwFm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184149OjpdbF3xB4u9koln.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Office Phone Booth by Framery</h3><p>在开放的办公室工作是不是觉得没办法静下心来工作？2010 年夏天，在科技公司实习的芬兰设计师 Samu Hällfors 和 Vesa-Matti Marjamäki 就因为上司打电话的声音太吵而提起了投诉，得到的回复却是“那就给我个电话亭”。有意思的是，正是这句话启发他们成立了名为 <a href=\"https://www.frameryacoustics.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Framery</a> 的初创公司，负责设计和制作具有隔音效果的室内“电话亭”。除了单人的小亭子之外，他们还推出了最多可容纳 4 人的“会议室”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184035nBpQTGwFxuAe42XR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184035I4Py58CKauHco2dv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.896250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184035sbBwDxLk7r6QOog5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.240000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: inherit; font-family: Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 冬青黑, STXihei, 华文细黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, SimSun, 宋体, Helvetica, Tahoma, &quot;Arial sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 20px; text-align: left;\">KFC for the fans! by four eight five</span></h3><p>在今年的超级橄榄球联赛（Super Rugby）上，五支新西兰球队的粉丝又多了一个为球队加油助威的道具：由创意公司 <a href=\"http://485design.co.nz/\" rel=\"nofollow\">485</a> 为联赛赞助商 KFC 设计的 KFC for the fans! 限量炸鸡桶。这些炸鸡桶的两侧分别印有其中一支球队的头盔和此次活动的宣传语，也让 KFC 多了一条宣传途径。为了更好地模拟出佩戴头盔的效果，头盔侧还专门裁出了一道缺口。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184204upJLG84Xy1jDnUaE.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184204HvcD2iGWze4thUJS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184204Msp4nquJEXyV5m8g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ECO Cycle by Giken</h3><p>随着越来越多的人开始选择自行车作为代步工具，在停放空间本来就不宽裕的大城市难免会出现乱停放的问题。日本工程公司技研制作所（Giken）为此想到了利用地下空间这一解决办法，借助独创的压入技术，建造了能够自动停放自行车的地下车库。这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.giken.com/en/solutions/underground_developments/eco_cycle/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ECO Cycle</a> 的车库看起来就像是将地面上的立体车库放到了地下，而且还无需看管。车主只要将车停放在入口的插槽，再刷一下专用的储值卡就能启动停放的流程，取出时也只要输入密码即可，平均仅耗时 13 秒。据悉，目前<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/technology/eco-cycle-automated-underground-parking-bicycles-japan-08-08-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本境内已建成 50 多座 ECO Cycle</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184220IqLJZrTeBhR3fw6N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713542\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184220cHwOm5fLDZ2Csanh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184220yCx9DfATt1Maj5F2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184220rOPMT1IfGn7mZgbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713542\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sole Impressions by Ben Polkinghorne &amp; Scott Kelly</h3><p>你留心过那些留在花瓣上的脚印吗？当一对英国设计师好友 <a href=\"http://scottandbenorbenandscott.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ben Polkinghorne 和 Scott Kelly</a> 无意间发现玉兰花的花瓣与鞋底的形状颇为相似后，他们决定利用足印制作一套用花瓣表示的鞋子图鉴。今年春天，他们找来了包括 Nike Jordan Academy 和 Converse Chuck Taylors 在内的 11 双著名的鞋款，穿上它们在收集来的玉兰花花瓣上创作出了独特的印记。目前这些限量 100 张的印刷品正在伦敦的 <a href=\"https://www.thearchivistsgallery.com/collections/frontpage/products/sole-impressions\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Archivist’s Gallery</a> 和格拉斯哥的 <a href=\"https://subversiongallery.co.uk/products/scott-and-ben-sole-impressions-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Subversion Gallery</a> 出售，售价为 100 英镑。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184356ipLv6z4WnYPVDFQq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184356lV0cwCTJYpOHx3RP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170809184357hUPleI9VGrwFtzn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}